{
    "publish_date": "2012-03-13T10:55:15.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT9M51S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I would like to introduce our next speaker of the night:", 
            "dur": "2.659", 
            "start": "3.553"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Vik Nithy.", 
            "dur": "1.706", 
            "start": "6.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He is a young man who has already founded", 
            "dur": "2.336", 
            "start": "7.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "three companies at the age of twenty.", 
            "dur": "1.651", 
            "start": "10.254"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sorry, I was about to say twenty companies \nat the age of three.", 
            "dur": "3.025", 
            "start": "11.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is after being diagnosed", 
            "dur": "3.472", 
            "start": "14.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "post-HAC with a number of conditions.", 
            "dur": "3.789", 
            "start": "18.402"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So he&#39;s a truly inspiring young enterpreneur", 
            "dur": "2.621", 
            "start": "22.191"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he is going to tell you why we procrastinate.", 
            "dur": "2.051", 
            "start": "24.812"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.114", 
            "start": "26.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "3.965", 
            "start": "27.977"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I finished high school about two years ago.", 
            "dur": "2.512", 
            "start": "37.499"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And although I did fairly well,", 
            "dur": "2.187", 
            "start": "40.011"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t do nearly as well as I could have done", 
            "dur": "2.208", 
            "start": "42.198"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if I didn&#39;t suffer from a chronic", 
            "dur": "2.333", 
            "start": "44.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "debilitating addiction to procrastination.", 
            "dur": "3.801", 
            "start": "46.739"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would put off studying until the night before", 
            "dur": "2.724", 
            "start": "50.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every assignment and every exam wherever possible.", 
            "dur": "2.579", 
            "start": "53.264"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is anyone else guilty of cramming?", 
            "dur": "2.997", 
            "start": "55.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah. So you probably know how it feels", 
            "dur": "2.457", 
            "start": "58.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to maybe take a five-minute Facebook break", 
            "dur": "1.982", 
            "start": "61.297"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "before you start working and then", 
            "dur": "2.692", 
            "start": "63.279"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "realize that three hours have gone past,", 
            "dur": "3.008", 
            "start": "65.971"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or promise yourself that you&#39;ll start working tomorrow", 
            "dur": "2.607", 
            "start": "68.979"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every day for a week. Tomorrow, tomorrow.", 
            "dur": "3.326", 
            "start": "71.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not just studying that we procrastinate on,", 
            "dur": "2.368", 
            "start": "74.912"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we procrastinate on things like doing chores,", 
            "dur": "2.408", 
            "start": "77.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we procrastinate on thinking about our future,", 
            "dur": "4.359", 
            "start": "79.688"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we procrastinate on \nsaving money and getting fit.", 
            "dur": "5.204", 
            "start": "86.278"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think procrastination is a really serious problem,", 
            "dur": "3.108", 
            "start": "91.482"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s about not being able to bring ourselves", 
            "dur": "2.218", 
            "start": "94.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to do the things that we know we want to do.", 
            "dur": "2.635", 
            "start": "96.808"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So tonight I&#39;m going to talk to you about", 
            "dur": "1.931", 
            "start": "99.443"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the reasons why we procrastinate", 
            "dur": "1.737", 
            "start": "101.374"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then hopefully give you some tips \non how to overcome it", 
            "dur": "3.322", 
            "start": "103.111"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you can get around to doing that.", 
            "dur": "2.175", 
            "start": "106.433"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "108.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Okay.", 
            "dur": "1.209", 
            "start": "114.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, procrastination is not a disease.", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "117.365"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s more about the decisions that you make,", 
            "dur": "3.366", 
            "start": "119.465"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the decision not to do what you need to do now", 
            "dur": "2.934", 
            "start": "122.831"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but to do it later instead.", 
            "dur": "2.551", 
            "start": "125.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s really like you&#39;re having \nan argument in your head, isn&#39;t it?", 
            "dur": "2.892", 
            "start": "129.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One part of you wants to work", 
            "dur": "1.616", 
            "start": "132.268"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "another part of your brain \nwants to play Angry Birds.", 
            "dur": "2.613", 
            "start": "133.884"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for some reason \nyou always manage to convince yourself,", 
            "dur": "2.689", 
            "start": "136.497"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh it&#39;s okay, I can do \nwhatever I need to do tomorrow,", 
            "dur": "3.026", 
            "start": "139.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t need to do it now.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.254", 
            "start": "142.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So as a psychology student", 
            "dur": "1.231", 
            "start": "144.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have the opportunity to find out \nwhat exactly is going on", 
            "dur": "2.743", 
            "start": "145.697"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "inside our brains when we procrastinate.", 
            "dur": "2.642", 
            "start": "148.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I found that there actually is \nan argument in our heads", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "151.082"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "between the limbic system and the prefrontal cortex.", 
            "dur": "3.438", 
            "start": "154.232"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, this is the prefrontal cortex.", 
            "dur": "2.114", 
            "start": "164.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the part of our brain that tells us:", 
            "dur": "1.745", 
            "start": "166.612"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;You should be working Vik, you have \na 40% assignment due tomorrow.&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.444", 
            "start": "168.357"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a higher level part of your brain;", 
            "dur": "2.966", 
            "start": "172.801"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the other part of your brain \ninvolved in procrastination", 
            "dur": "4.236", 
            "start": "175.767"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the limbic system.", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "180.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this is a more primitive part of your brain", 
            "dur": "2.858", 
            "start": "181.873"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that wants to watch another episode of Gossip Girl", 
            "dur": "2.596", 
            "start": "184.731"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "before you start studying.", 
            "dur": "2.005", 
            "start": "187.327"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So why is that the limbic system", 
            "dur": "1.804", 
            "start": "189.332"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "always seems to win the argument?", 
            "dur": "2.214", 
            "start": "191.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The answer lies \nin this deceptively cute part of the brain", 
            "dur": "3.415", 
            "start": "194.873"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "called the amygdala.", 
            "dur": "1.784", 
            "start": "198.288"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The amygdala is a part of your brain", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "200.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that controls fear and anxiety", 
            "dur": "2.562", 
            "start": "202.842"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the fight-of-flight response \nto threatening stimulus.", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "205.404"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for example, if you are in a jungle", 
            "dur": "2.674", 
            "start": "208.474"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you see a wild lion in the distance,", 
            "dur": "2.562", 
            "start": "211.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what do you do?", 
            "dur": "1.963", 
            "start": "213.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have no idea, I&#39;ve never seen a wild lion", 
            "dur": "2.741", 
            "start": "215.673"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I have seen a teacher approach me", 
            "dur": "2.284", 
            "start": "218.414"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when I haven&#39;t done my homework.", 
            "dur": "1.675", 
            "start": "220.698"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "0.926", 
            "start": "222.373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I think the response \nin the amygdala is quite similar:", 
            "dur": "2.684", 
            "start": "223.299"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The first thing you do is freeze;", 
            "dur": "3.089", 
            "start": "225.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your palms get sweaty, \nyour heart starts beating fast", 
            "dur": "3.066", 
            "start": "229.072"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and your prefrontal cortex, \nthe decision maker shuts down.", 
            "dur": "3.194", 
            "start": "232.138"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because if you see a wild lion in the jungle,", 
            "dur": "2.224", 
            "start": "235.347"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you don&#39;t want a voice in your head to remind you", 
            "dur": "2.085", 
            "start": "237.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you have an essay to write,", 
            "dur": "2.333", 
            "start": "239.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you have to focus on \nwhat&#39;s going on in the world around you", 
            "dur": "3.223", 
            "start": "241.989"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and responding to physiological needs.", 
            "dur": "3.47", 
            "start": "245.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, when we procrastinate,", 
            "dur": "2.485", 
            "start": "248.682"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we experience a mild anxiety response", 
            "dur": "3.229", 
            "start": "251.167"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to a theatening stimulus which just happens to be", 
            "dur": "2.721", 
            "start": "254.412"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an assignment that you may have to complete.", 
            "dur": "2.545", 
            "start": "257.133"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, what is it that we&#39;re afraid of?", 
            "dur": "2.792", 
            "start": "260.787"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is it that we are afraid of? \nWell, meet your monkey mind!", 
            "dur": "3.653", 
            "start": "265.378"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the part of your brain,", 
            "dur": "1.983", 
            "start": "269.031"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the voice in your head that reacts \nto the threatening stimulus of an essay.", 
            "dur": "5.768", 
            "start": "271.014"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You may be afraid of an overwhelming --", 
            "dur": "2.736", 
            "start": "276.782"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You might find that the task is overwhelming", 
            "dur": "2.643", 
            "start": "279.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you don&#39;t know where to start.", 
            "dur": "2.137", 
            "start": "282.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You might -- if it&#39;s an unpleasant task,", 
            "dur": "2.184", 
            "start": "287.099"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you might dread the displeasure of doing the task,", 
            "dur": "3.094", 
            "start": "289.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and if it&#39;s a more complex task with a --", 
            "dur": "4.723", 
            "start": "292.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when your performance is being measured", 
            "dur": "1.653", 
            "start": "297.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then you may have a fear of actual failure.", 
            "dur": "2.711", 
            "start": "298.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So perfectionists use procrastination", 
            "dur": "2.279", 
            "start": "301.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as a self-handicapping tool to avoid", 
            "dur": "4.938", 
            "start": "303.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "personal failure.", 
            "dur": "1.287", 
            "start": "308.681"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for example, if you have \nan assignment due on Friday,", 
            "dur": "3.473", 
            "start": "309.968"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it&#39;s Monday today, \nyou can finish the assignment tomorrow.", 
            "dur": "3.912", 
            "start": "313.441"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you don&#39;t do well,", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "317.353"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then what does it say about \nyour capacity to do well in the exams.", 
            "dur": "3.147", 
            "start": "319.311"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Whereas if you start on Thursday night and cram", 
            "dur": "3.826", 
            "start": "322.458"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then if you fail, it&#39;s just because \nyou&#39;re lazy and you crammed.", 
            "dur": "3.314", 
            "start": "326.284"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re not stupid, you&#39;re perfectly normal.", 
            "dur": "2.729", 
            "start": "329.598"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, your prefrontal cortex,", 
            "dur": "1.752", 
            "start": "334.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it knows that this is a stupid decision.", 
            "dur": "2.627", 
            "start": "336.188"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know that failure \nis a positive learning experience", 
            "dur": "4.458", 
            "start": "338.815"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that it&#39;s better to be safe than sorry.", 
            "dur": "2.265", 
            "start": "343.273"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But remember that your amygdala \nis about subconscious reactions.", 
            "dur": "6.152", 
            "start": "345.538"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So how can we overcome procrastination", 
            "dur": "3.965", 
            "start": "354.951"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if we have a monkey in our brains \nmaking decisions on our behalf?", 
            "dur": "4.637", 
            "start": "358.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The answer is something called &quot;metacognition&quot;:", 
            "dur": "3.916", 
            "start": "363.553"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thinking about thinking.", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "367.469"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we have to acknowledge that", 
            "dur": "1.392", 
            "start": "371.539"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we aren&#39;t gonna be the ones making the decision", 
            "dur": "1.797", 
            "start": "372.931"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to study tomorrow.", 
            "dur": "1.289", 
            "start": "374.728"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re gonna have this spontaneous lazy monkey", 
            "dur": "3.586", 
            "start": "376.017"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "making decisions on our behalf", 
            "dur": "1.507", 
            "start": "379.603"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we&#39;re too scared to do it ourselves.", 
            "dur": "2.585", 
            "start": "381.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there is a few things that we have to plan", 
            "dur": "1.819", 
            "start": "383.695"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in order to overcome this:", 
            "dur": "2.848", 
            "start": "385.514"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We have to plan goals.", 
            "dur": "1.633", 
            "start": "388.362"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So plan exactly what you need to do,", 
            "dur": "2.064", 
            "start": "389.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "split it up into parts, and we find that", 
            "dur": "2.936", 
            "start": "392.059"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the task is a lot less overwhelming \nfor all in a monkey.", 
            "dur": "4.493", 
            "start": "394.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Plan time. So figure out exactly", 
            "dur": "2.709", 
            "start": "399.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what you&#39;re gonna get done in what time frame", 
            "dur": "2.084", 
            "start": "402.197"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and remember guys,", 
            "dur": "1.423", 
            "start": "404.281"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this is not something you need to do \neverytime you need to study,", 
            "dur": "2.709", 
            "start": "405.704"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this is just something that you need \nto get into the habit of doing automatically", 
            "dur": "4.032", 
            "start": "408.413"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you realize that \nyou need to get something done.", 
            "dur": "3.391", 
            "start": "412.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Plan resources.", 
            "dur": "1.671", 
            "start": "415.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So if you spend ten minutes before you start working", 
            "dur": "2.435", 
            "start": "417.507"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to get everything you need in the table in front of you,", 
            "dur": "2.745", 
            "start": "419.942"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can&#39;t go ahead and later convince yourself that", 
            "dur": "2.632", 
            "start": "422.687"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you need to use Google", 
            "dur": "1.328", 
            "start": "425.319"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or you need to go on Facebook to get something", 
            "dur": "2.282", 
            "start": "426.647"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because everything you need is in front of you.", 
            "dur": "2.844", 
            "start": "428.929"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Plan the process. So research has shown that", 
            "dur": "3.555", 
            "start": "432.419"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you visualize the process of doing something,", 
            "dur": "2.465", 
            "start": "435.974"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the task becomes easier to do.", 
            "dur": "2.681", 
            "start": "438.439"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you close your eyes \nand think about what you need to do,", 
            "dur": "3.509", 
            "start": "441.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then, you brain is tricked \ninto thinking that you&#39;ve done it before", 
            "dur": "3.002", 
            "start": "444.629"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it becomes so much easier to get things done.", 
            "dur": "4.035", 
            "start": "447.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Plan for distractions: \nso you know that you monkey mind", 
            "dur": "3.132", 
            "start": "451.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is gonna wanna check Facebook every five minutes.", 
            "dur": "2.502", 
            "start": "454.798"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to make a commitment to stay focused", 
            "dur": "3.181", 
            "start": "457.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and not get distracted.", 
            "dur": "1.828", 
            "start": "460.481"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And lastly plan for failure.", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "464.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, say you&#39;re doing a maths problem", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "465.562"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you come to a question that you can&#39;t do:", 
            "dur": "2.109", 
            "start": "467.942"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this is usually the time", 
            "dur": "1.754", 
            "start": "470.051"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when people decide to take a five-minute break!", 
            "dur": "2.941", 
            "start": "471.805"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know that the saying &quot;Don&#39;t give up!&quot; is clich\u00e9", 
            "dur": "2.819", 
            "start": "474.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I think that when it comes to roadblocks", 
            "dur": "2.985", 
            "start": "477.565"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we are trying to do something", 
            "dur": "1.173", 
            "start": "480.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s especially relevant,", 
            "dur": "1.42", 
            "start": "481.723"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it&#39;s not just while we are studying,\nit&#39;s in every part of life.", 
            "dur": "3.137", 
            "start": "483.143"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If we procrastinate when we come to a roadblock,", 
            "dur": "2.291", 
            "start": "486.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then I don&#39;t think we&#39;re ever gonna get around to", 
            "dur": "2.576", 
            "start": "488.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "solving the problem.", 
            "dur": "1.422", 
            "start": "491.147"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to learn \nto grind your teeth and get through it.", 
            "dur": "3.295", 
            "start": "492.569"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh dear!", 
            "dur": "1.011", 
            "start": "495.864"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, this quote said:", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "496.875"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Don&#39;t wait. The time will never be just right.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.654", 
            "start": "500.805"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it&#39;s by Napoleon Hill.", 
            "dur": "1.612", 
            "start": "503.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I think, as students, the number one reason \nwhy we tend to procrastinate", 
            "dur": "4.812", 
            "start": "505.071"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is because we don&#39;t think \nthe conditions are perfect for proactivity.", 
            "dur": "5.664", 
            "start": "509.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We wait until the weekend to write an essay,", 
            "dur": "3.538", 
            "start": "515.547"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we wait until we&#39;re in the &quot;zone&quot; to be creative,", 
            "dur": "2.969", 
            "start": "519.085"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we wait until we have money to give to charity...", 
            "dur": "2.615", 
            "start": "522.054"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think that if we get into the habit of planning,", 
            "dur": "3.566", 
            "start": "524.669"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "thinking about thinking and getting things done quickly", 
            "dur": "3.768", 
            "start": "528.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then the world becomes our oyster", 
            "dur": "2.353", 
            "start": "532.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and our future will become a lot more prosperous.", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "534.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you.", 
            "dur": "1.212", 
            "start": "537.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "2.267", 
            "start": "538.442"
        }
